ial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2800" dirty="0"/><a:t>Polycyclic disease </a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="342900" indent="-342900" algn="just"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2800" dirty="0"/><a:t>How to reduce disease incidence, x, at any point in the epidemic: </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2800" dirty="0"><a:highlight><a:srgbClr val="FFFF00"/></a:highlight></a:rPr><a:t>Reduce initial inoculum, Q (monocyclic) Xo (Polycyclic).</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="342900" indent="-342900" algn="just"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2800" dirty="0"><a:highlight><a:srgbClr val="FFFF00"/></a:highlight></a:rPr><a:t>Reduce rate constant, R.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="342900" indent="-342900" algn="just"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="2800" dirty="0"><a:highlight><a:srgbClr val="FFFF00"/></a:highlight></a:rPr><a:t>Reduce duration of epidemic, t.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree><p:extLst><p:ext uri="{BB962C8B-B14F-4D97-AF65-F5344CB8AC3E}"><p14:creationId xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main" val="1893399930"/></p:ext></p:extLst></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:sld>